June Martel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/June_Martel 0 June Martel (November 19, 1909 – November 23, 1978) was a singer and a stage and motion picture actress from Chicago, Illinois. She was a petite brunette who weighed only a bit more than one hundred pounds.
